extendedInfo.description: This app has been abandoned please download the new versionElance Job Feed v2https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dreamcarved.elancejobfeedv2&hl=enThis app lets you select a job category from elance and then grabs the rss job feeds and displays them so you can easily view a potential job to bid on taking you to the actual site to login and bid. -No login Required to view jobsNote: No advanced api functionally involved with this app this is strictly for viewing elance job feeds for a fast quick way to check out a job.
